#!icon=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/luestr/IconResource/main/App_icon/120px/MailMaster.png
#!date=2025-05-13 15:17:08
[Rewrite]
======== 开屏配置 ========
^https://appconf.mail.163.com/mailmaster/api/http/urlConfig.do$ reject-dict
======== conf.do 页面配置清理 ========
去除：会员引导、功能运营浮层、活动Tab、主账号运营、侧边付费横幅、
邮积分/commonFuncList、添加邮箱(10005)、注册邮箱(10006)、通讯录(10008)、AI工具箱(10011)
^https://appconf.mail.163.com/mailmaster/api/page/v2/conf.do$ response-body-json-jq 'del(.data.memberOperator, .data.functionOperatorInfoList, .data.activityTabInfoList, .data.masterOperatorList, .data.extList.mineSideBanner, .data.commonFuncList, (.data.newCommonFuncList[]? | select(.strategyId | IN(10005, 10006, 10008, 10011))))'
======== function.do 功能列表清理 ========
侧滑工具栏彻底清空
删除：Function-AD、Function-Score-CardConfig、Function-Task-Center、Function-NPS-Config
^https://appconf.mail.163.com/mailmaster/api/config/function.do$ response-body-json-jq '(.data.config[] | select(.functionName == "Function-Drawer-Tools").result.tools) |= [] | del(.data.config[] | select(.functionName | test("^Function-(AD|Score-CardConfig|Task-Center|NPS-Config)$")))'
======== 任务中心 ========
^https://dashi.163.com/task-center-api/fapi/task/(list|overview)$ reject-dict
======== 运营浮层 ========
^https://appconf.mail.163.com/mailoperating/mailmaster/api/operator/get$ reject-dict
======== vm.mail.163.com 弹窗 & 付费引导 ========
^https://vm.mail.163.com/api/mkt/dialogInfo reject-dict
^https://vm.mail.163.com/api/pay/ reject-dict
[MitM]
hostname=appconf.mail.163.com, dashi.163.com, vm.mail.163.com
